{
  "id": "RAW_b0fdda",
  "title": "AI 编程终结的不是代码，而是作为「容器」的软件",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg5NTc0MjgwMw==&mid=2247516595&idx=2&sn=91de18724315855f59d9fe7064ca18e0",
  "date": "2025-06-03 12:57:00",
  "author": "范阳",
  "siteName": "Founder Park",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <section style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;\">\n   <a class=\"weapp_image_link js_weapp_entry\" data-miniprogram-type=\"image\" style=\"\" data-miniprogram-appid=\"wxfd634fac70ce584e\" data-miniprogram-path=\"pages/home/dashboard/index\" data-miniprogram-nickname=\"AGI Playground 2025\" data-miniprogram-servicetype=\"0\" data-miniprogram-applink=\"#小程序://AGIPlayground2025/DuT2CtczflZGKFE\" data-miniprogram-imageurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/qpAK9iaV2O3sgqllQmlwtMqrfvG9jqJPgfzSW6iaJvl3iaNHed1COftdDuwicFmYQNhcK4yGcwJNpmuQkSn4ZI06qg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\"><br></a>\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2005 年 YouTube 的「上传」按钮开启了内容创作的民主化时代。而现在，AI 以「描述」这一动词，正在改变我们对于软件的认知与生产方式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">去年，知名硅谷投资人、Pace Capital 创始合伙人 Chris Paik 发布了一篇名为</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg5NTc0MjgwMw==&amp;mid=2247499209&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=af37004b3431e9fe835ae4fb1124a29d&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"《软件的终结》\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">《软件的终结》</a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的文章，在文章中 Chris Paik 大胆提出了一个预测：大型语言模型将把软件的边际成本压至趋近于零，就像互联网对「内容」做的那样。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一年后，这个预测逐渐应验。Chris Paik 近期再次发布了一篇博客文章《无限代码的黎明》，顺着这个方向，提出随着大语言模型（LLM）将代码生成的成本降至趋近于零，传统意义上作为独立「应用程序」或「平台」存在的软件形式将逐渐消失。这篇文章的最核心观点是：软件的终结并非代码的死亡，而是其作为「容器」的消融。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">以下为文章原文，内容略有调整。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 149, 158);\"><em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">原文链接：</span></span></em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 149, 158);\"><em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Dm9UrhgaRMu_DjOz5KluO7ibOsPaUVQgwnC5-ccw9_g/mobilebasic</span></span></em></span></p><ul style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n  </ul>\n  <hr style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;transform:scale(1, 0.5);border-right-width:0px;letter-spacing:0.578px;border-bottom-width:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);transform-origin:0px 0px;border-style:solid;border-left-width:0px;\">\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:16px 0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-hig