:rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.5px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><br></span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:16px 0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.5px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">软件真正的终结</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.5px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">不是代码的死亡，</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:16px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.5px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">而是其「容器」的消融</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2010 年后出生的小孩从未翻开过报纸。很快，他们可能也永远不会点开应用程序。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">历史告诉我们：当内容可以自由流动，承载它的容器终将淡出。报纸让位给了网页，CD 被流媒体取代。现在，传统意义上的「软件」也成了下一个要被抛弃的容器。当逻辑可以随时调用、随意拼接，容器便不复存在，留下的只有功能本身。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这才是软件真正的终结：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不是代码的死亡，而是其容器的消融。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">功能被彻底释放，无处不在，触手可及——无限的能力，无限的代码。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;line-height: 1.5em;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1a987884-bb1a-4801-865f-08135793bf00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.679174484052533\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"533\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100005293\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1a987884-bb1a-4801-865f-08135793bf00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;line-height: 1.5em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">注：上面 meme 图里的第二个需求经过这么多年以后，基本解决，下一个问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "AI 编程将软件代码边际成本降至零，软件作为独立应用的「容器」形式将消融，功能无处不在。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "AI 编程将软件代码边际成本降至零，软件作为独立应用的「容器」形式将消融，功能无处不在。",
  "summary": "文章探讨了 AI 大语言模型对软件形态的深刻影响。借鉴 YouTube 将内容生产门槛降至“上传”的例子，作者 Chris Paik 提出，AI 通过“描述”这一新的交互方式，正将代码生成成本推向零，使得传统意义上的软件“应用程序”或“平台”等容器形式逐渐消融。工作重点从“怎么写代码”转变为“想要什么功能”。在代码无限供给的时代，分发优势不再，系统响应速度成为关键。最终，用户将不再需要点开特定应用，功能将无处不在，信任将成为最稀缺的资源。软件的未来在于功能的流转与组合，而非固定的容器。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 将代码生成成本降至趋近于零",
      "explanation": "类似互联网使内容生产成本极低，AI 通过理解“描述”即可生成代码，极大降低了软件开发的门槛和成本。"
    },
    {
      "point": "软件作为独立“容器”的形式正在消融",
      "explanation": "当代码和功能随需生成、组合，用户无需依赖特定 App，功能将成为无处不在的服务，打破传统软件的边界。"
    },
    {
      "point": "在“无限代码”时代，信任成为最稀缺资源",
      "explanation": "随着技术变得不透明但结果高效，用户将更依赖能够快速响应并值得信赖的智能代理或系统进行决策和执行。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "大语言模型将把软件的边际成本压至趋近于零，就像互联网对「内容」做的那样。",
    "AI 给了我们一个新动词：描述，于是那些拥有五百人专攻单一功能的公司瞬间蒸发。",
    "当成本持续下降，我们的注意力会向上游寻找「稀缺」。最上层是信任------这是时间累积起来的信誉，决定了某个代理是否有权代表我们做决定。",
    "这才是软件真正的终结：不是代码的死亡，而是其容器的消融。",
    "功能被彻底释放，无处不在，触手可及------无限的能力，无限的代码。"
  ],
